                self.crawl(url, callback=self.find_login_page)

i want to find all the "Login page" of "www.baidu.com", however, from the code you can see it maybe goes into a deep recusive(recusively call function find_login_page), so i want to control the recusive level such as recusively crawl 3 levels, what should i do?

Thanks in advance!

